## 4ï¸âƒ£ Common DP-700 Exam Traps ğŸš¨

| Trap                                        | Correct Thinking                          |
|---------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Event-based = exactly-once                  | âŒ Only tumbling window guarantees this   |
| Schedule triggers are real-time             | âŒ They are polling-based                 |
| File updates trigger events                 | âŒ Usually only create events             |
| Time zone doesnâ€™t matter                    | âŒ Always UTC                             |
| One trigger can watch many storage accounts | âŒ One location per trigger               |

